AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000069> "Magnetic power loss at 1.0 T / 400 Hz is a total magnetic power loss that has been determined at 1.0 T of maximum magnetic induction B and 400 Hz of frequency of alternating magnetic field"@en)
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000069> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0009007> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000070> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000009> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000008> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001931> ObjectAllValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000039> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UO_0000106>) DataHasValue(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> "400"^^xsd:integer))))) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000009> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000008> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020127> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000051> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001931> ObjectAllValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000039> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UO_0000228>) DataHasValue(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> "1.0"^^xsd:decimal))))))))))
